  "type": "Toggle",
  "display_name": "Infiltration",
  "display_fullname": "Pool Invisibility Invisibility",
  "display_help": "You blend into your environment and swiftly make your way while attempting to stay undetected. Infiltration grants you a considerable boost to both your jump height and run speed. Even if discovered, you are hard to see and have a bonus to Defense from all attacks. If, however, you attack while using this power, you will be discovered and will lose your Stealth and Defense bonus provided by this power.<br><br>Infiltration can be active at the same time as other running and jumping toggles, but only the strongest run speed buff and strongest jumping buff will apply.",
